messages.content: What does the ComfyUI_KytraWebhookHTTP node do?

The ComfyUI_KytraWebhookHTTP node utilizes Moviepy to convert and send images or videos to a webhook endpoint directly from ComfyUI. It is intended for personal use in discord and can be used with any valid webhook URL.
Can I use the ComfyUI_KytraWebhookHTTP node for a different webhook URL other than discord?
Yes, the ComfyUI_KytraWebhookHTTP node is not restricted to discord and can be used with any valid webhook URL.
